<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<title>Pets Page</title>

	<!-- Pre-requisite Meta Tags -->
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="description" content="Pets page showing the pets." />
	<meta name="keywords" content="Wishlist, Orders, Pets" />
	<meta name="author" content="Kenzo, Lawrenz, John Cee, Jericho, George" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />

	<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
	<link href="~/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" media="all" />
</head>

<body class="bg-white font-sans">

    <main class="w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">

        <!-- Top Section -->
        <div class="container px-4 py-5 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-5 justify-center items-center lg:items-start">

            <!-- Image Section (Thumbnails + Main) -->
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-4">

                <!-- Thumbnails -->
                <div class="flex flex-row lg:flex-col gap-2 order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="p-1">
                        <img class="w-20 h-20 object-cover cursor-pointer rounded-md" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-1">
                        <img class="w-20 h-20 object-cover cursor-pointer rounded-md" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-1">
                        <img class="w-20 h-20 object-cover cursor-pointer rounded-md" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-1">
                        <img class="w-20 h-20 object-cover cursor-pointer rounded-md" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Main Image -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <i class="bi bi-caret-left text-3xl cursor-pointer"></i>
                    <img class="w-[320px] sm:w-[400px] md:w-[480px] lg:w-[500px] h-auto rounded-md object-cover" src="~/images/Skibidi.png" />
                    <i class="bi bi-caret-right text-3xl cursor-pointer"></i>
                </div>
            </div>


            <!-- Details Section -->
            <div class="mt-6 lg:mt-0 px-4 pt-4 pb-2 w-full max-w-lg border-2 rounded-lg border-[#684034] flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-[#684034] text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center font-bold pt-4">Skibidi</h3>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-black">
                        <span class="font-bold">By: Woolly Friends</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-black">
                        <h4 class="text-center">Uploaded 1 day ago</h4>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-black pt-4 font-bold">
                        <h4 class="text-green-700 text-2xl">&#8369;5,000</h4>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-black">Breed:</h3>
                        <h3 class="text-black">Aspin</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-black">Gender:</h3>
                        <h3 class="text-black">Male</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-black">Date of Birth:</h3>
                        <h3 class="text-black">October 10, 2024</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-black">Location:</h3>
                        <h3 class="text-black">Pureza, Manila</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="py-3 flex justify-center text-center">
                    <a href="~/PaymentForm/Index" class="mr-2 bg-[#684034] text-white border border-[#8B8381] text-lg min-w-[180px] rounded-md py-3 px-6 hover:bg-[#5e3a2f]">
                        Buy Me
                    </a>
                    <a href="~/AdoptionForm/Index" class="bg-[#684034] text-white border border-[#8B8381] text-lg min-w-[180px] rounded-md py-3 px-6 hover:bg-[#5e3a2f]">
                        Adopt Me
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom Section -->
        <div class="mt-10 border-2 border-[#684034] rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">Description:</h3>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-justify text-black text-lg">
                <p>
                    Skibidi is a beautiful, timid boy who takes a while (couple of weeks) to warm up to people and would suit a smaller family without children.
                    After becoming comfortable he is very affectionate and likes cuddles on the couch.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Skibidi is a very smart boy. He learned to sit and drop within two weeks and walks on a lead quite well without pulling.
                    He's friendly with all dogs, not so keen on children, and hasn’t been tested with cats.
                </p>
                <p>
                    He would suit a home that already has another dog and has a large backyard as he loves to play and prefers to be outside.
                </p>
                <p>
                    All inquiries, questions, and interest in adoption need to be via the link below — please provide detailed responses
                    to the application questions highlighting how your home and lifestyle suit the needs of the dog you are applying for.
                    Don’t forget to check your spam or junk folder for a reply.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <script src="~/js/main.js"></script>
</body>


</html>